'''Krzysztof Buras''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.
Buras has competed as Krzystof Buras.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (1) 2014 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>


===Runners-up===

* [[World Transnational Open Teams Championship]] (1) 2009 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/transnational-open-teams.aspx World Transational Open Teams Winners]</ref>

* [[World Team Olympiad|World Olympiad Teams Championship]] (1) 2012

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (3)
